&lt;h2 id=&#34;问题&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#问题&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 问题&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li class=&#34;quiz&#34;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;From the first two paragraphs, we learn that &lt;span class=&#34;gap&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&#34;options&#34;&gt;
&lt;li class=&#34;correct&#34;&gt;the townsfolk deny the RSC&#39;s contribution to the town&#39;s revenue.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;the actors of the RSC imitate Shakespeare on and off stage.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;the two branches of the RSC are not on good terms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;the townsfolk earn little from tourism.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ul class=&#34;options&#34;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;✔️ 无中生有&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;❌ 文章没有说他们是如何演戏的&lt;/li&gt;
