&lt;li&gt;the sightseers do more shopping than the playgoers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;the playgoers go to no other places in town than the theater.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ul class=&#34;options&#34;&gt;
