&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&#34;quiz&#34;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;By saying &amp;quot;Stratford cries poor traditionally&amp;quot; (Line 2, Paragraph 4), the author implies that &lt;span class=&#34;gap&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&#34;options&#34;&gt;
