&lt;p&gt;But particularly when viewed against America’s turbulent past, today’s social indices hardly suggest a dark and deteriorating social environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;语法-22&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#语法-22&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 语法&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;But particularly &lt;ins&gt;when viewed against America’s turbulent past&lt;/ins&gt;, &lt;ins&gt;today’s social indices&lt;/ins&gt; &lt;ins class=&#34;dot warming&#34;&gt;hardly suggest&lt;/ins&gt; &lt;ins class=&#34;wavy&#34;&gt;a dark and deteriorating social environment.&lt;/ins&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
